                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_8690">كليله و دمنه</title>
                     <note>Written on the instructions of John Romer.(A pencilled note on the verso of the leaf preceding the text states that the first page is wanting.) Second of 8 blank folios before text, recto: a) Signature of Jno Romer. b) Description of the work in English. Folio following text, recto: stamp, the name and date filled in in ink 'Presented to the ROYAL ASIATIC SOCIETY by John Romer Esq. I April 1837. Rendering into Persian of the Ibn al-Muqaffa''s Arabic rendering of the Fables if Bidpai. Headings and punctuation in red.</note>
